constraints_details.result: Hinterland Lower Lea Valley including Stratford

description: Demolition of all existing structures on the site (excluding Pelican Cottage) and the erection of 86 new dwellings (11 x studio, 25 x 1 bedroom, 29 x 2 bedroom, 18 x 3 bedroom, 2 x 4 bedroom & 1 x 5 bedroom), including affordable housing, in a building extending to between 2 to 9 storeys in height, together with the provision of associated access, basement plant room, landscaping and infrastructure works.  Alterations and partial demolition in connection with the refurbishment of Pelican Cottage.
